Note:
Runa Standard Library: Primitive Types

Primitive types (Integer, Float, String, Boolean, None) are built-in to the Runa language.

Type checking is performed using the 'is of type' operator:
    Assert value is of type Integer

Type retrieval is performed using the 'type of' expression:
    Let t be type of value

This module exists for documentation and reference only; no additional processes are required.
:End Note 